CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 10, 1945, pg. 4, reads: "Feted - A birthday party was given for one-year-old Samuel Jones, Jr. of Monticello Street. He is the son of Corp. Samuel Jones, Sr. who is stationed somewhere in New Guinea. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Children gathered around one-year-old Samuel Jones Jr. seated on table with three cakes for birthday party in Jones home, Monticello Street
